quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  76,26,"E jemma he cujjan mbo cubahinanɗaa mbo jehma juutɗo."
  76,27,"Pellet ɓe na njiɗi nguurndam aduna njaawɗam gasde ɗam ɓe ngacca caggal mum en ñalawma nisɗo."
  76,28,"Ko minen tagi on min cemmbini terɗo si min kaajaama min ngostoroo on nandadiiɓe mon gostogol."
  76,29,"Ko nde woni waajo goongo kala paalaaɗo daɗde nanngira fa'ade e joomiiko ruttorde."
  76,30,"On paaletaake si wonaAlla haaje pellet Alla ko ganndo ko ñeeño"
  76,31,"Homo naatna mbo o welaa e yurmeene makko o heblanii tooñɓe ɓe lepte mu'usɗe."
  77,1,"Mi wooɗndirii keneeli dewandirɗi hono sirka puccu."
  77,2,"E (keneeli)bippooji bippugol."
  77,3,"E carooji ɗi cargolo."
  77,4,"E ceerndooji ɗi ceerndugol."
  77,5,"E tellinooji ɗi wahyu."
  77,6,"Gantingol maa jeertingol."
  77,7,"Gooŋɗi podante ɗon ko, ko goongo."
  77,8,"Ñande koode ɗe momta."
  77,9,"Si kammu o huuɓtaama"
  77,10,"Si pelle ɗe nawaama."
  77,11,"Saanga nelaaɓe ɓe kappana waktu."
  77,12,"E ñalawma oon dirtinaaɗo."
  77,13,"Wonan'de ñalngu ceerndugol."
  77,14,"Holko anndinatma ma ñalngu ceerndugol."
  77,15,"Nden ñalnde, bone woodanii yedduɓe ɓeen."
  77,16,"Mbele min kalkaani adinooɓe ɓe."
  77,17,"Refti mn ndewni heen sakkatiiɓe ɓe."
  77,18,"Ko hono nih nin mbaɗata bonɓe ɓe."
  77,19,"Nden ñalnde, bone woodanii yedduɓe ɓeen."